---

---

<!-- Step by Step Section -->
<section class="py-24 bg-white relative overflow-hidden">
    <style>
        .step-timeline-line {
            position: absolute;
            left: 50%;
            top: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            width: 2px;
            background-image: linear-gradient(
                to bottom,
                #cbd5e1 50%,
                transparent 50%
            );
            background-size: 2px 20px;
            background-repeat: repeat-y;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            z-index: 0;
        }
    </style>

    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 relative z-10">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
            <h2
                class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-ultimate-blue font-heading"
            >
                Step by Step <span class="text-ultimate-navy"
                    >Ikut Placement Test</span
                >
            </h2>
            <p
                class="text-ultimate-navy/70 mt-2 font-body font-light max-w-xl mx-auto"
            >
                Yuk ikuti setiap langkahnya untuk hasil yang maksimal!
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="relative max-w-4xl mx-auto">
            <!-- Timeline line (desktop) -->
            <div class="step-timeline-line hidden md:block"></div>

            <div class="space-y-10">
                <!-- Step 1 -->
                <div
                    class="relative z-10 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center group"
                >
                    <div
                        class="w-full bg-white rounded-3xl p-6 shadow-soft hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300 border border-slate-100 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-8 relative overflow-hidden"
                    >
                        <div
                            class="w-full md:w-1/3 h-44 bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center relative shrink-0 overflow-hidden"
                        >
                            <div
                                class="absolute top-3 left-3 bg-white/90 backdrop-blur-sm text-ultimate-blue font-bold text-lg px-3 py-1 rounded-xl shadow-sm z-20"
                            >
                                01
                            </div>
                            <img
                                src="/steps/step1.png"
                                alt="Mulai Placement Test"
                                class="w-full h-full object-contain"
                            />
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex-1 text-center md:text-left">
                            <h3
                                class="text-xl font-bold text-ultimate-navy mb-2 font-heading"
                            >
                                Mulai Placement Test
                            </h3>
                            <p
                                class="text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed font-body"
                            >
                                Klik tombol mulai untuk memulai perjalananmu
                                hari ini. Evaluasi kemampuan awal kamu secara
                                gratis untuk mengetahui <em>starting point</em> belajarmu.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Step 2 -->
                <div
                    class="relative z-10 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center group"
                >
                    <div
                        class="w-full bg-white rounded-3xl p-6 shadow-soft hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300 border border-slate-100 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-8 relative overflow-hidden"
                    >
                        <div
                            class="w-full md:w-1/3 h-44 bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center relative shrink-0 overflow-hidden"
                        >
                            <div
                                class="absolute top-3 left-3 bg-white/90 backdrop-blur-sm text-ultimate-yellow font-bold text-lg px-3 py-1 rounded-xl shadow-sm z-20"
                            >
                                02
                            </div>
                            <img
                                src="/steps/step2.png"
                                alt="Lengkapi Data Diri"
                                class="w-full h-full object-contain"
                            />
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex-1 text-center md:text-left">
                            <h3
                                class="text-xl font-bold text-ultimate-navy mb-2 font-heading"
                            >
                                Lengkapi Data Diri
                            </h3>
                            <p
                                class="text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed font-body"
                            >
                                Berikan informasi terbaikmu agar kami dapat
                                memberikan analisis yang akurat. Data ini
                                penting untuk pemetaan personalisasi
                                pembelajaran.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Step 3 -->
                <div
                    class="relative z-10 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center group"
                >
                    <div
                        class="w-full bg-white rounded-3xl p-6 shadow-soft hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300 border border-slate-100 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-8 relative overflow-hidden"
                    >
                        <div
                            class="w-full md:w-1/3 h-44 bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center relative shrink-0 overflow-hidden"
                        >
                            <div
                                class="absolute top-3 left-3 bg-white/90 backdrop-blur-sm text-ultimate-yellow font-bold text-lg px-3 py-1 rounded-xl shadow-sm z-20"
                            >
                                03
                            </div>
                            <img
                                src="/steps/step3.png"
                                alt="Kerjakan Tesnya"
                                class="w-full h-full object-contain"
                            />
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex-1 text-center md:text-left">
                            <h3
                                class="text-xl font-bold text-ultimate-navy mb-2 font-heading"
                            >
                                Kerjakan Tesnya
                            </h3>
                            <p
                                class="text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed font-body"
                            >
                                Fokus dan berikan jawaban yang paling tepat
                                dalam 15–20 menit. Tidak perlu tegang, kerjakan
                                santai untuk hasil yang mencerminkan kemampuan
                                aslimu.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Step 4 -->
                <div
                    class="relative z-10 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center group"
                >
                    <div
                        class="w-full bg-white rounded-3xl p-6 shadow-soft hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300 border border-slate-100 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-8 relative overflow-hidden"
                    >
                        <div
                            class="w-full md:w-1/3 h-44 bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center relative shrink-0 overflow-hidden"
                        >
                            <div
                                class="absolute top-3 left-3 bg-white/90 backdrop-blur-sm text-ultimate-blue font-bold text-lg px-3 py-1 rounded-xl shadow-sm z-20"
                            >
                                04
                            </div>
                            <img
                                src="/steps/step4.png"
                                alt="Dapatkan Hasil Tes"
                                class="w-full h-full object-contain"
                            />
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex-1 text-center md:text-left">
                            <h3
                                class="text-xl font-bold text-ultimate-navy mb-2 font-heading"
                            >
                                Dapatkan Hasil Tes
                            </h3>
                            <p
                                class="text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed font-body"
                            >
                                Skor band IELTS kamu akan langsung terukur
                                secara real-time. Lihat seberapa jauh progresmu
                                dan area mana yang perlu ditingkatkan lebih
                                lanjut.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Step 5 -->
                <div
                    class="relative z-10 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center group"
                >
                    <div
                        class="w-full bg-white rounded-3xl p-6 shadow-soft hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300 border border-slate-100 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-8 relative overflow-hidden"
                    >
                        <div
                            class="w-full md:w-1/3 h-44 bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center relative shrink-0 overflow-hidden"
                        >
                            <div
                                class="absolute top-3 left-3 bg-white/90 backdrop-blur-sm text-ultimate-blue font-bold text-lg px-3 py-1 rounded-xl shadow-sm z-20"
                            >
                                05
                            </div>
                            <img
                                src="/steps/step5.png"
                                alt="Rekomendasi Belajar"
                                class="w-full h-full object-contain"
                            />
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex-1 text-center md:text-left">
                            <h3
                                class="text-xl font-bold text-ultimate-navy mb-2 font-heading"
                            >
                                Rekomendasi Belajar
                            </h3>
                            <p
                                class="text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed font-body"
                            >
                                AI kami akan memberikan rencana belajar yang
                                sesuai dengan skor impianmu dan target kampus.
                                Kurikulum yang dipersonalisasi khusus untukmu.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Step 6 -->
                <div
                    class="relative z-10 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center group"
                >
                    <div
                        class="w-full bg-white rounded-3xl p-6 shadow-soft hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300 border border-slate-100 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-8 relative overflow-hidden"
                    >
                        <div
                            class="w-full md:w-1/3 h-44 bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center relative shrink-0 overflow-hidden"
                        >
                            <div
                                class="absolute top-3 left-3 bg-white/90 backdrop-blur-sm text-ultimate-yellow font-bold text-lg px-3 py-1 rounded-xl shadow-sm z-20"
                            >
                                06
                            </div>
                            <img
                                src="/steps/step6.png"
                                alt="Konsultasi Expert"
                                class="w-full h-full object-contain"
                            />
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex-1 text-center md:text-left">
                            <h3
                                class="text-xl font-bold text-ultimate-navy mb-2 font-heading"
                            >
                                Konsultasi Expert
                            </h3>
                            <p
                                class="text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed font-body"
                            >
                                Tanya apa saja kepada expert kami untuk
                                persiapan kuliahmu di luar negeri. Dapatkan
                                insight berharga langsung dari para ahli
                                pendidikan.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
